Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132766,133634}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133634,135002}We're here, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135002,137804}All right, let's go.\NThat's the counter attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.74,Title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:140507,145746}{\fad(200,0)\blur0.7}A kickoff to the world!{NOTE:世界へむけてキックオフ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146646,148482}Try to come at me from both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148782,150317}Gotcha, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150317,151918}Remember, no pushing.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166933,168335}We're almost at the goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171471,174841}Hikaru, I'll assist you,\Nand you shoot from the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176376,177744}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179379,180414}He missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180414,181948}You shot it too high…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197831,199366}An overhead kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199366,200434}Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200434,201868}As expected from Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204404,205472}Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209409,212279}Hey! It's you pipsqueaks again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212279,213480}Sorry, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213480,216016}Here's the scary goalkeeper…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216016,217651}Game over, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217651,219486}See you at school tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219486,221555}Good luck with the practice. Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221555,223356}Ciao! Till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223356,225859}Next time I won't be so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225859,227494}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231398,233266}How's your form today, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233266,234734}It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234734,238472}If you keep at it, you'll become\Na professional player in no time, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238472,239639}You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239639,242442}Cheering from the bench\Nin the next game again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242442,244077}Don't let it get to you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245479,246546}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246546,248548}I'll be on my way, sir!{NOTE:he says the character name?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256490,257858}Hey, Toto.{NOTE:not sure about dog's name}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263029,265665}That dog doesn't have\Nan ounce of decency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265665,268168}Whenever it gets hungry\Nit comes fawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268168,269903}I'm home, Ms. Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269903,272706}Good morning.\NDinner will soon be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272706,274241}Don't take too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309009,309476}{\i1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311778,313046}It's yours, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315081,316016}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317384,319119}Move! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325592,326826}It was awesome, Julien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328495,329729}Listen well, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330363,333867}The best San Podesta Junior\Nstriker is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333867,336803}Your role is to pass me the ball,\Nand I do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338638,341541}You're Japanese.\NIt's just a fun game to you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341541,343510}Just keep low profile\Nand it'll be all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345946,346780}Julien…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349382,351218}Don't let it get to you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352152,353153}Thanks, Mario.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353954,355355}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361094,364264}Hey, I figured I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364264,368335}What are you impressions?\NDo you see any future talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369069,376476}San Podesta's club team is famous\Nnot only in Italy, but also in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376476,378812}I would say that it is quite likely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378812,382716}that some of this club's juniors\Nwill join the ranks of world-class players.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382716,384484}They're the elite, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384484,387888}Can't blame you if you can't\Ndecide on any individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387888,389956}If I had to name some of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389956,394094}my attention is drawn to Mario,\Nand Julien who transferred from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395395,398765}They're something different.\NI'm sure you'll notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400133,403904}Or maybe you were thinking\Nof someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410510,412879}You can't possibly be thinking\Nof that Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413580,416182}He's been on the bench\Nfor a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416983,419519}Geez, Mr. Robson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419519,421421}You're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421421,425725}The patients at the clinic\Nare all waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426359,428495}Sorry, sorry.\NI'll be there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428495,429763}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429763,433433}I agree that the Italian boys\Nare eons ahead in terms of technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433433,438571}However, I have never seen anyone\Nplay soccer so freely, have so much fun at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439472,443043}He's so young, and he's already one\Nwith the ball both in mind and the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449115,452552}If he gets hooked on it,\NI'm sure that in the future…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452786,453720}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455188,457624}Ah, I was just thinking out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457624,460360}Yes.\NYou're thinking too much, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461494,465966}I'd understand if he took karate or ninjutsu,\Nbut a Japanese, playing soccer? Fat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467067,468535}Maybe you're right, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469369,472005}That's enough.\NSir, you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472005,475742}Don't hold me responsible\Nif the patients wither away or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476976,478211}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489856,493460}{\i1}That Japanese boy…\NHe's named Hikaru, if I recall correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502902,504571}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504904,506306}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507540,510377}Teach… Teach us soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510377,514447}I want to join\NSan Podesta Junior next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514447,516216}Then we can play with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518184,520020}Anything's wrong, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520820,524691}Next week, my aunt is coming\Nback from Japan to take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525325,527794}What? You're going back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527794,530964}But you came here to Genua\Nto study soccer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532966,537036}My dad used to work in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537670,539672}He loved this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540573,545445}So when I told him I wanted to study\Nsoccer abroad, he agreed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547947,551017}But… about half a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551017,555555}when my parents were en route\Nfrom Japan to see me here in Italy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555555,558858}both Dad… and Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573206,576943}Now Auntie wants\Nto take me back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577744,581247}She's a good aunt.\NShe's really worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582115,583249}But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583249,584884}Don't go, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584884,585919}Yeah, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585919,589022}Stay and teach us soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589022,593226}I want to study European\Nsoccer more, much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593226,596062}Not just European.\NBrazilian and Argentinean soccer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596062,599999}And one day, to have soccer friends\Nfrom all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600834,602569}That is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603803,605171}{\i1}That is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605972,609342}{\i1}If he gets hooked on it,\NI'm sure that in the future…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611511,613713}I don't want to go back, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613713,615482}I like all of my friends here in Genua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616516,619953}I want to stay here\Nand study soccer more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619953,621488}That's the spirit, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622489,626192}You'll stay here in Italy,\Nand continue to play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626192,627727}Who… Who are you, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629162,632132}I'm a dreamer, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632132,636236}Don't worry about anything.\NLeave everything to old Bertini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639706,641574}I appreciate his enthusiasm, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645311,647947}Can that old man do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652185,653386}What do you say, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654087,656689}I have to convince\NHikaru's aunt somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656689,659726}Could you take him\Nunder your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659726,662929}and make him into\Na world-class player?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662929,664764}I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664764,667166}Aren't you forgetting\Nsomething, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668468,672405}Mr. Robson is a doctor.\NHe doesn't teach soccer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673273,678044}When it comes to soccer, I know\Nmuch more than him. Right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678044,679546}Stay out of this, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681447,685318}I am not talking to\NDr. Robson right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687053,693526}I am talking to England's legendary\Nace striker, Albert Robson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707507,709208}All patched up.\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709208,711678}Don't make your mom worry anymore\Nand stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711678,712312}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712912,714414}Mister Robson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714414,719619}I'll have you know that I have no intention\Nof going home until I hear your reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719619,722322}This is a hospital!\NKeep your voice low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723289,724724}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724724,729729}You said yourself that Hikaru is\Nvery promising when you saw him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729729,731130}So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731130,734968}I promised to never get\Ninvolved with soccer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734968,736836}Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736836,740440}You were absolute favorites for that\NWorld Cup, yet just before it started
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740440,742675}you, the unbeatable ace of the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742675,746512}disappeared from the world of soccer\Nwithout so much as a word of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747313,749916}I don't know what\Nare your circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749916,755221}the fact remains that Hikaru\Nneeds your power to stay in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755221,759525}Or are you saying that\Nyou've truly given up on soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759525,762262}Doctor has never\Ngiven up on soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762262,766933}I know it the best that\Nhe was an exceptional player.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767734,768735}Anna…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768735,770203}But he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770203,775808}Your eyes look completely different\Nwhenever you see Hikaru play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775808,777677}Even if you retired,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778344,782982}I can see it perfectly well that\Nthis boy has reminded you of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786052,787253}Doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794260,795595}Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795595,797797}Oh? You've finished already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800333,804370}Tomorrow's the day\Nyour auntie will pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805872,810777}I appreciate Auntie's\Nconcern about me, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810777,811844}I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811844,813446}Me neither, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813446,816182}It is very difficult for me\Nto let you go, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816916,819085}But stay positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819085,823289}I'm praying that you could stay\Nhere with us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826192,827160}Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829362,830630}Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830630,833032}Hikaru! How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834167,837170}Well, well!\NAre you his aunt, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837170,838538}Mr. Bertini!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838538,840340}Hikaru, who is this mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840340,842742}Well, Mr. Bertini is, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842742,846346}Oh, I'm terribly sorry.\NI forgot to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846346,849849}I was caught off\Nby a Japanese beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851284,854387}Come in, come in.\NIt's a bit dirty, but make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858257,863496}Hikaru, Señorita and I have\Nsome adult stuff to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865598,867900}What does he mean,\N"a bit dirty"? Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869502,873039}Because of my line of work,\NI've seen kids from many different teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873806,877710}But it's the first time I've seen a child\Nwith such a great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878444,884150}I'm sure that under my guidance\NHikaru would make it to the Europe's,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884150,888454}no, the world's best.\NThat's the kind of potential he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890990,894293}Do you understand, Señorita?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894293,901267}It's no wonder Hikaru doesn't want to go back\Nto Japan. You're the one who's deceived him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901734,903336}Deceive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903336,908007}I was able to tell at a glance\Nwhether you were a trustworthy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908808,913513}Do you seriously think I could leave Hikaru\Nin hands of a man such as yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913513,915281}Hikaru is going back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915281,917784}– Can we discuss—\N– No, we cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917784,920920}What an unreliable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920920,924824}Besides, who leaves a 11-years-old\Nalone in a foreign country
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924824,926959}just so that he can play soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926959,930163}It's unheard of!\NDon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930163,933466}But Auntie, I'm not alone at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933466,936102}But… But, Hikaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936102,940239}As long as I have this ball, I can\Nbecome friends with anyone, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941240,943009}I don't even need words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943876,945478}This ball is all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946212,951350}You can make plenty of friends back home,\Neven without a soccer ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952051,953119}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953119,957623}One year ago, Hikaru's parents\Ncame here to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958291,965264}They told me that ever since he was little,\Nas long as he had a ball, he was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965932,969869}Even when his father had\Nto work abroad more than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969869,972038}contrary to his parents' fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972038,976843}Hikaru would make tons of friends,\Nall thanks to this soccer ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977777,982648}I can't imagine what he'd be going through\Nif he was forced to say goodbye to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983749,990022}Soccer is a wonderful gift\Nthat God gave to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990857,992959}That's what his parents told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993559,995261}Dad… Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995261,998598}That's right.\NHikaru was born with a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998598,1001667}I knew his parents\Nwould understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001667,1004871}You're forgetting the fact\Nthat I am his family right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005538,1007373}This conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007874,1010643}I am talking Hikaru\Nto the hotel right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010643,1012311}W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012311,1015948}I won't listen to anybody telling me\Nhow to raise my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015948,1017917}I will send someone\Nto get your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017917,1019385}Auntie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023222,1025658}P-Please reconsider, Señorita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027493,1029295}Ah, thank god we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029295,1030463}Robson!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030463,1033232}We would be here much earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033232,1034667}but we had a surprise patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035368,1036736}Thank goodness you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037236,1041474}Your presence is worth a thousand words.\NLet me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042108,1047246}This man is said to have the longest career\Nin the history of world soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047246,1050516}He is former England's ace striker,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050516,1052184}Albert Robson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061160,1063763}I read about you\Nin soccer books, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064297,1066465}You're the legendary ace striker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066465,1068334}Hikaru, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068334,1072705}Doctor is willing to coach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072705,1074574}For real, Mr. Robson!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074574,1077009}No matter who you are,\Nnothing will change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077009,1078945}We're going, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078945,1080780}Wait, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080780,1082848}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083416,1084350}Guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084984,1085985}Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085985,1087520}Are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087520,1089922}Don't go anywhere.\NPlease stay with us…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089922,1093359}– Hikaru, don't go…\N– Do you really have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094360,1097530}Please talk some sense to her.\NDr. Robson!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097530,1098497}Anna…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098497,1101167}This is not happening.\NMy dreams…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106672,1107840}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107840,1111077}Somebody…\NSomebody stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114080,1115181}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120486,1122188}Somebody save that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130763,1131864}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141607,1142708}{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149749,1151117}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151117,1152985}Amazing! Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153519,1154987}What a feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154987,1156856}I… I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181113,1182381}Hikaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182381,1186585}Hikaru can do such\Namazing things with that ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187153,1188721}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188721,1192291}That ball is a source\Nof tremendous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193426,1200566}This little ball holds the hope and dreams\Nof many people thorough the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201400,1207640}And Hikaru just proved to us\Nwhat miracles he can do with that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212078,1215081}Will you leave Hikaru under my care?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222021,1224290}– That was so close.\N– Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224290,1227626}– Thank goodness.\N– You were so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231397,1236268}So can I really stay in Italy\Nand continue playing soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236268,1239672}Yes. It's just like your dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240406,1244443}It's no use trying to pull the ball\Nout of your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244443,1249715}Your dad dreamed of forming\Na bridge between Japan and the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249715,1251383}and became a diplomat\Nfor this reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251383,1255521}Who knows? Maybe you'll be able\Nto realize that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256122,1257623}Through your beloved soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258524,1260493}He's got what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260493,1264663}And he's got me,\Nold Bertini at his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269935,1272238}I'll be cheering for you from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272671,1273606}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273606,1274406}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274406,1276342}Thank you, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276342,1278778}Don't worry about Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278778,1280446}Please take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282414,1284150}Stay safe, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284884,1287386}You be careful too, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295094,1297796}Goodbye, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298464,1299965}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310242,1312611}We did it, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312611,1313846}Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:22:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313846,1320219}I'm a cheap guy who finds kids and introduces\Nthem to the club team to earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320219,1322855}But when I met you,\Nsomething clicked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322855,1326091}and now I want to chase dreams\Nnot thinking about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327092,1328527}Mr. Bertini…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328527,1332264}It's just like you said, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332264,1335901}You'll make tons of friends\Nthorough the world some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335901,1340940}It won't matter who they're from,\Nwhat country they belong to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340940,1345711}And together, you'll make a team\Nthat the world hasn't seen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345711,1349949}And you'll not only become\Na legendary ace striker,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349949,1353219}you'll become\Nthe best striker in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353619,1355120}The best striker…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.82,0:22:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355821,1360392}But know this, Hikaru. The path\Nto accomplish your dreams is not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361093,1364363}Are you ready for my training?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364363,1368167}Of course, Mr. Robson.\NI mean, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368167,1373272}Let me help you along the way.\NSee, I love soccer as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373272,1375574}My name's Anna.\NNice to meet you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375574,1377276}Thanks. Pleasure's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380246,1381914}All right. Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407773,1409708}My training has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409908,1414113}But Mr. Robson doesn't\Nlet me touch the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414113,1416815}Instead, he makes me do\Nall sorts of weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417716,1420386}But I want to get good at soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421487,1423789}Next time on Moero Top Striker:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424556,1426292}"Aim to be the world's best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427293,1430796}A kickoff to our dreams!
